data.text:
Serbia

Population 6.8 million

Serbia is a candidate country for European Union membership. The EU is Serbias primary political and economic partner, and its largest provider of financial assistance. To support Serbia on its path towards EU membership, the EU and Serbia are working closely to meet EU standards. This covers many areas  from strengthening the rule of law and countering corruption, to improving human rights and the business environment.

In parallel, the EUs financial support in fields like environmental protection, infrastructure, business competitiveness, education, culture and more, are bringing benefits and opportunities for Serbian citizens.
